lemma (in Order) fixp_same:"\<lbrakk>W1 \<subseteq> carrier D; W2 \<subseteq> carrier D; t \<in> W1; b \<in> carrier D; ord_isom (Iod D W1) (Iod (Iod D W2) (segment (Iod D W2) b)) g; \<forall>u\<in>segment (Iod D W1) t. fixp g u\<rbrakk> \<Longrightarrow> segment (Iod D W1) t = segment (Iod D W2) (g t)"
